 is perfect for them!\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The deal\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Too much chat and not enough (limited) action.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Too much chat and not enough (limited) action\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am barely bothered with this compared to before.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"#BBCOlympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"#BBCOlympics\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While another questioned: \\\"Anyone else annoyed at the BBC coverage of the Olympics?\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1561, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.8631900720792148, \"rank\": 0.15849338014427822, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"Anyone\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They spend most of it talking and switching channels, show you athletics events after they have already happened, and now the golf has just been cut off for cycling and the news\\u2026 can not even get it on iPlayer?\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"channels\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"at